The Canadians, looking for a record fifth consecutive title,
will now have to take on Slovakia in quarterfinal play on
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Russia finished atop the group B standings with an undefeated
record of three wins and a tie and, like the United States,
received an automatic bye to the semifinals.
</P>
<P>
In the other group B action, Finland closed out round robin
play with a 4-3 win over Slovakia, leaving them second in the
group standings.
</P>
<P>
