non-communist parties.
</P>
<P>
On behalf of the CPC Central Committee, Jiang congratulated He
Luli, chairperson of the Central Committee of Revolutionary
Committee of the Chinese Kuomintang, Ding Shisun, chairman of the
Central Committee of China Democratic League, and Cheng Siwei,
chairman of the Central Committee of China Democratic National
Construction Association.
</P>
