non-communist parties, replacing the old core with new leadership
in the three parties, something that once again shows that the
non-communist parties in the country have made good progress in
improving themselves including efforts made organizationally,
and that there is no lack of successors of the non-communist
parties."
</P>
<P>
Strengthening multi-party cooperation under the leadership of
the Chinese Communist Party is significant, he added, and said
that there is a fine tradition of major leaders of the CPC Central
Committee maintaining unity and friendship with leaders of the
non-communist parties.
</P>
<P>
During the past decades of revolution and construction, he
said, the non-communist parties working shoulder to shoulder
with the Chinese Communist party made great contributions to the
victory in China's new democratic revolution and the socialist
cause.
</P>
