<HEADLINE> 5 Rebels Killed in Eastern Sri Lanka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, January 1 (Xinhua) -- At least five Tamil rebels were
killed today when they confronted government troops in Eastern
province of Sri Lanka, according to a military news release.
</P>
<P>
