<TEXT>
<P>
FREETOWN, January 1 (Xinhua) -- folday Sankoh, the
revolutionary united front (RUF) leader today reassured that he
is committed to the peace process and the civil war in Sierra
Lone has been over.
</P>
<P>
This is contained in his new year greetings to President Tejan
Kabbah, the government and the people of Sierra Leone dispatched
from Abidjan, Cote di'voire.
</P>
<P>
